[Leak-free Toilet Tank]: The toilet tank is stable and leak-free, which is convenient for your daily use and can play a good role in saving water.

Water and Energy Savings: Maximum gallons per flush is 0.8/1.6 gallons per minute. With a two-speed flush design, its flush system uses low-flow technology to reduce water consumption. Compared with the traditional toilet, it can greatly reduce the water consumption and contribute to environmental protection and energy saving.
